Jiang Praises Sino-Russian Regular Meeting Mechanism 
Visiting Chinese President Jiang Zemin on Tuesday praised the regular
meeting mechanism between the Chinese premier and the Russian prime
minister.
During a meeting with Russian Prime Minister Mikhail Kasyanov at the
Russian governmental building, Jiang said Chinese Premier Zhu Rongji
will visit Moscow in September for the sixth regular meeting, at which
he is expected to hold discussions with his Russian counterpart
Kasyanov on a wide range of issues related to bilateral cooperation.
He said the mechanism of regular meetings between the Chinese premier
and the Russian prime minister provided important guarantee for
pragmatic cooperation between the two sides.
The scope of this mechanism has been expanded and the cooperation
deepened, Jiang said. He predicted broader and deeper mutually
beneficial cooperation between the two countries.
Jiang, on the third day of his four-day state visit to Russia, also met
with Russian Federal Council Speaker Yegor Stroyev on Tuesday.
